1
00:01:34,650 --> 00:01:40,850
[Shadow Love]

2
00:01:41,710 --> 00:01:43,930
[Episode 6]

3
00:02:20,380 --> 00:02:21,380
Don't move.

4
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:32,400
Your shoulder wound hasn't healed.

5
00:02:33,590 --> 00:02:36,920
Could it be related to
the vanished supernatural strength?

6
00:02:40,840 --> 00:02:41,800
Don't move.

7
00:02:43,470 --> 00:02:45,100
You seem to be different.

8
00:03:24,280 --> 00:03:25,400
So...

9
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:27,680
all those hurtful words you said that day,

10
00:03:27,680 --> 00:03:28,940
trying to push me away,

11
00:03:30,120 --> 00:03:31,400
was because

12
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:34,430
you wanted to pull me out of this mess?

13
00:03:38,510 --> 00:03:39,970
But did you ever think that

14
00:03:40,079 --> 00:03:41,680
from the moment you picked me up,

15
00:03:41,680 --> 00:03:43,560
brought me back to your residence,

16
00:03:43,560 --> 00:03:45,710
and learned the secret of my body,

17
00:03:45,870 --> 00:03:47,600
I was already part of this game?

18
00:03:48,870 --> 00:03:50,120
In court intrigues,

19
00:03:50,590 --> 00:03:51,820
a single misstep

20
00:03:51,840 --> 00:03:53,240
could cost you your life.

21
00:03:53,520 --> 00:03:55,650
You don't even remember your own past.

22
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:57,310
How could you possibly understand

23
00:03:57,310 --> 00:03:58,430
its complexity?

24
00:04:01,190 --> 00:04:03,190
This matter is indeed complicated.

25
00:04:04,520 --> 00:04:06,230
But I did kill Huo Du.

26
00:04:06,380 --> 00:04:08,030
If turning me in can solve the problem,

27
00:04:08,030 --> 00:04:09,430
just do it.

28
00:04:12,710 --> 00:04:14,190
If I turn you in...

29
00:04:18,590 --> 00:04:19,470
you'll die.

30
00:04:22,090 --> 00:04:22,950
Are you scared?

31
00:04:23,310 --> 00:04:24,150
I fear death,

32
00:04:24,760 --> 00:04:26,560
but I'm not afraid to die for you.

33
00:04:28,370 --> 00:04:29,140
Otherwise,

34
00:04:29,850 --> 00:04:31,310
I wouldn't have come back.

35
00:04:32,430 --> 00:04:33,720
You keep saying

36
00:04:34,519 --> 00:04:35,640
you can't leave me.

37
00:04:36,029 --> 00:04:37,180
Why?

38
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:42,730
Yessterday, you were in a coma,

39
00:04:43,240 --> 00:04:44,950
but today you're perfectly fine.

40
00:04:44,950 --> 00:04:47,630
Is it because of Lu Xin's
exceptional medical skills?

41
00:04:47,630 --> 00:04:48,690
Or is it because...

42
00:04:49,040 --> 00:04:50,190
you drank my blood?

43
00:04:54,450 --> 00:04:55,770
That day we first met,

44
00:04:56,370 --> 00:04:58,310
when you were being chased
by the Yao Army,

45
00:04:58,310 --> 00:04:59,720
I felt a powerful force

46
00:04:59,720 --> 00:05:00,870
flow through me.

47
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:02,370
And from that moment on,

48
00:05:02,870 --> 00:05:04,630
I had this urge

49
00:05:04,630 --> 00:05:06,430
to protect you.

50
00:05:08,690 --> 00:05:10,130
You're saying that

51
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:12,560
from the day I found you,

52
00:05:13,630 --> 00:05:14,820
my blood

53
00:05:15,870 --> 00:05:17,510
bound us together?

54
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:19,830
I thought...

55
00:05:19,950 --> 00:05:21,590
all I needed was blood.

56
00:05:23,310 --> 00:05:24,630
But after last night,

57
00:05:25,800 --> 00:05:26,800
I realized...

58
00:05:28,430 --> 00:05:30,120
all I need is your blood.

59
00:05:31,070 --> 00:05:32,780
I depend on your blood,

60
00:05:32,800 --> 00:05:33,880
and your presence.

61
00:05:34,120 --> 00:05:35,320
Once I'm away from you

62
00:05:35,800 --> 00:05:37,730
or haven't seen you for a long time,

63
00:05:38,950 --> 00:05:41,070
I'll suffer a heart-piercing pain.

64
00:05:42,630 --> 00:05:45,160
That day you took me back
to the stone chamber,

65
00:05:45,270 --> 00:05:47,470
I vaguely remember hearing them say...

66
00:05:47,930 --> 00:05:48,930
Blood oath.

67
00:05:49,159 --> 00:05:50,220
If that's the case,

68
00:05:50,730 --> 00:05:52,260
why didn't you say anything

69
00:05:52,409 --> 00:05:54,540
when I tried to drive you away that day?

70
00:05:54,950 --> 00:05:56,210
I didn't say anything,

71
00:05:56,400 --> 00:05:58,000
because I didn't want to scare you.

72
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:58,750
I left

73
00:05:59,430 --> 00:06:00,870
because you wanted me to.

74
00:06:01,530 --> 00:06:02,680
Whatever you wish to do,

75
00:06:02,680 --> 00:06:04,159
I'll do my best to make it happen.

76
00:06:04,159 --> 00:06:05,950
Our blood oath may be real,

77
00:06:06,240 --> 00:06:07,770
but my desire to protect you

78
00:06:08,310 --> 00:06:09,390
is also real.

79
00:06:13,010 --> 00:06:14,250
If it frightens you,

80
00:06:15,390 --> 00:06:16,480
I'll leave again.

81
00:06:17,160 --> 00:06:18,120
Where would you go?

82
00:06:18,120 --> 00:06:19,780
If you die, would that be on me?

83
00:06:21,910 --> 00:06:23,910
So, you're worried about my safety.

84
00:06:24,420 --> 00:06:24,930
If it's because

85
00:06:24,930 --> 00:06:26,490
I took that strike for you,

86
00:06:27,070 --> 00:06:28,240
then it was worth it.

87
00:06:29,430 --> 00:06:31,360
You should focus on recovering first.

88
00:06:31,360 --> 00:06:32,360
We'll worry about

89
00:06:32,630 --> 00:06:33,680
the rest later.

90
00:06:35,720 --> 00:06:36,320
By the way,

91
00:06:39,480 --> 00:06:40,630
those flowers...

92
00:06:41,390 --> 00:06:42,520
they're beautiful.

93
00:06:43,860 --> 00:06:44,450
Wait,

94
00:06:51,010 --> 00:06:52,540
I want to verify something.

95
00:07:27,880 --> 00:07:28,730
General,

96
00:07:28,760 --> 00:07:29,710
as you ordered,

97
00:07:29,750 --> 00:07:31,120
the soldiers have been training hard,

98
00:07:31,120 --> 00:07:33,520
and not daring to slack off
for a single day.

99
00:07:36,190 --> 00:07:37,070
Report!

100
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:40,080
General,

101
00:07:40,100 --> 00:07:41,010
urgent news from the front line!

102
00:07:41,010 --> 00:07:42,470
The Yao Army is on the move.

103
00:07:44,650 --> 00:07:45,930
Our spy reported that

104
00:07:45,960 --> 00:07:46,610
the Yao Army

105
00:07:46,610 --> 00:07:48,659
has entered combat readiness.

106
00:07:49,110 --> 00:07:50,370
Under the cover of night,

107
00:07:50,370 --> 00:07:51,420
they're slowly

108
00:07:51,480 --> 00:07:53,340
advancing toward our borders.

109
00:07:53,370 --> 00:07:54,170
It seems

110
00:07:54,190 --> 00:07:56,040
they intend to launch a surprise attack.

111
00:07:56,040 --> 00:07:58,630
The Yao Army was defeated at Lucheng
less than a month ago.

112
00:07:58,630 --> 00:08:00,140
During this time of regime change,

113
00:08:00,140 --> 00:08:01,440
they suddenly sending out troops,

114
00:08:01,440 --> 00:08:02,590
and now is not

115
00:08:02,620 --> 00:08:04,080
a good time for them to start a war.

116
00:08:04,080 --> 00:08:04,740
It seems

117
00:08:04,770 --> 00:08:06,670
the Yao Army has
gotten the fake deployment map.

118
00:08:06,670 --> 00:08:08,600
Since the Yao Army is so desperate,

119
00:08:09,159 --> 00:08:11,159
we'll give it everything we've got.

120
00:09:10,460 --> 00:09:12,930
[General's Residence]

121
00:09:13,150 --> 00:09:14,440
Although we won

122
00:09:14,550 --> 00:09:15,910
this battle,

123
00:09:16,240 --> 00:09:17,510
the entire army,

124
00:09:17,510 --> 00:09:18,600
the soldiers' drills,

125
00:09:18,600 --> 00:09:19,510
the logistics management,

126
00:09:19,510 --> 00:09:20,750
and every little detail

127
00:09:20,750 --> 00:09:21,950
cannot be neglected.

128
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:23,030
The whole army

129
00:09:23,270 --> 00:09:25,000
must remain ready at all times.

130
00:09:26,240 --> 00:09:27,240
Understood.

131
00:09:37,670 --> 00:09:39,000
Is there anything else?

132
00:09:42,560 --> 00:09:43,590
General,

133
00:09:44,960 --> 00:09:46,490
you don't look well lately.

134
00:09:47,360 --> 00:09:48,080
Is that so?

135
00:09:48,790 --> 00:09:50,050
I hadn't noticed that.

136
00:09:52,150 --> 00:09:53,000
General!

137
00:09:53,310 --> 00:09:54,360
General!

138
00:09:55,870 --> 00:09:57,200
The Young Master

139
00:09:57,200 --> 00:09:58,100
is making a scene in the backyard!

140
00:09:58,100 --> 00:09:59,430
We can't handle him,

141
00:09:59,460 --> 00:10:01,650
please go there right away.

142
00:10:03,150 --> 00:10:03,880
You head back to camp first.

143
00:10:03,880 --> 00:10:04,520
Let's go.

144
00:10:21,440 --> 00:10:23,680
To the fallen soldiers of Taijin...

145
00:10:23,720 --> 00:10:25,410
Happy New Year!

146
00:10:25,600 --> 00:10:26,360
Come get your money!

147
00:10:26,360 --> 00:10:27,320
Young Master!

148
00:10:27,320 --> 00:10:28,440
Happy New Year!

149
00:10:28,440 --> 00:10:29,360
Over there.

150
00:10:29,360 --> 00:10:30,050
Soldiers!

151
00:10:31,510 --> 00:10:32,460
Money's here!

152
00:10:32,560 --> 00:10:33,690
Come get your money!

153
00:10:35,610 --> 00:10:37,470
-Here, take the money.
-General!

154
00:10:37,480 --> 00:10:38,240
General!

155
00:10:38,670 --> 00:10:40,270
Please go talk to Young Master.

156
00:10:40,270 --> 00:10:40,910
If this continues,

157
00:10:40,910 --> 00:10:42,670
he'll burn the house down!

158
00:10:43,600 --> 00:10:45,000
Happy New Year!

159
00:10:45,630 --> 00:10:46,360
Soldiers!

160
00:10:46,360 --> 00:10:47,000
What are you going to do?

161
00:10:47,000 --> 00:10:48,030
Kick over the fire basin

162
00:10:48,030 --> 00:10:48,720
and beat him again?

163
00:10:48,720 --> 00:10:49,720
What else can I do?

164
00:10:49,930 --> 00:10:51,480
I thought he would reflect on his actions,

165
00:10:51,480 --> 00:10:53,010
but he's only gotten worse.

166
00:10:53,830 --> 00:10:55,190
Someone

167
00:10:55,370 --> 00:10:56,430
claims to

168
00:10:56,890 --> 00:10:58,470
treat soldiers like family,

169
00:10:58,470 --> 00:11:00,550
but forgets about you on holidays!

170
00:11:00,630 --> 00:11:01,360
Soldiers!

171
00:11:01,380 --> 00:11:02,930
If you become vengeful ghosts,

172
00:11:02,930 --> 00:11:04,480
don't let her off the hook!

173
00:11:04,510 --> 00:11:05,390
Soldiers!

174
00:11:05,440 --> 00:11:06,830
It's not like you haven't hit him before.

175
00:11:06,830 --> 00:11:07,570
Did it help?

176
00:11:08,130 --> 00:11:09,460
If you hit him, it only hurts you too.

177
00:11:09,460 --> 00:11:10,780
Grab more clothes!

178
00:11:10,810 --> 00:11:11,970
Buy more things.

179
00:11:13,000 --> 00:11:15,430
Since you know so much about
getting along with people,

180
00:11:15,430 --> 00:11:16,960
and you were once a kid yourself,

181
00:11:16,960 --> 00:11:17,550
you go.

182
00:11:18,080 --> 00:11:18,630
Me?

183
00:11:18,840 --> 00:11:19,840
You don't want to?

184
00:11:20,280 --> 00:11:21,320
I can't hit him or scold him,

185
00:11:21,320 --> 00:11:22,440
and you won't go talk to him.

186
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:23,080
Fine.

187
00:11:23,320 --> 00:11:25,040
Let him burn the whole residence down.

188
00:11:25,040 --> 00:11:26,520
Then we'll be homeless.

189
00:11:26,970 --> 00:11:29,030
Are we going to be homeless together?

190
00:11:29,600 --> 00:11:30,720
Soldiers,

191
00:11:30,740 --> 00:11:31,950
come get your money!

192
00:11:31,980 --> 00:11:32,820
Just you.

193
00:11:33,520 --> 00:11:34,550
Annoying Li Ting!

194
00:11:34,570 --> 00:11:35,850
Take some silver

195
00:11:35,910 --> 00:11:37,870
and buy yourselves nice things.

196
00:11:38,120 --> 00:11:39,150
Alright, alright, you may leave now.

197
00:11:39,150 --> 00:11:40,120
Yes, sir.

198
00:11:41,840 --> 00:11:43,240
It's chaotic down there.

199
00:11:43,420 --> 00:11:44,910
I'll burn some

200
00:11:45,300 --> 00:11:46,560
handy weapons for you,

201
00:11:46,920 --> 00:11:48,280
and this jar of wine.

202
00:11:48,310 --> 00:11:50,740
It's the finest liquor.

203
00:11:50,910 --> 00:11:52,110
It's cold down there,

204
00:11:52,370 --> 00:11:53,230
drink more wine

205
00:11:53,240 --> 00:11:54,370
to warm yourselves.

206
00:12:03,360 --> 00:12:04,840
You knew it was dangerous,

207
00:12:04,950 --> 00:12:06,430
why didn't you tell me?

208
00:12:07,670 --> 00:12:09,470
Would it have made
any difference if I told you?

209
00:12:09,470 --> 00:12:10,930
You're making such a big scene,

210
00:12:10,930 --> 00:12:13,080
just to get Li Shuang's attention, right?

211
00:12:13,080 --> 00:12:14,540
Something this dangerous

212
00:12:15,340 --> 00:12:16,650
is exactly what you wanted.

213
00:12:16,650 --> 00:12:17,800
That's nonsense!

214
00:12:18,630 --> 00:12:20,670
Why would I want her attention?

215
00:12:21,030 --> 00:12:23,030
She calls me immature

216
00:12:23,390 --> 00:12:24,440
and reckless.

217
00:12:24,670 --> 00:12:26,080
She just doesn't know...

218
00:12:26,480 --> 00:12:27,600
that I care more about

219
00:12:27,600 --> 00:12:29,080
those fallen soldiers than she ever could.

220
00:12:29,080 --> 00:12:31,070
If you really care that much,

221
00:12:31,480 --> 00:12:32,750
show some sincerity.

222
00:12:33,030 --> 00:12:34,740
Burn something more valuable
than these incense.

223
00:12:34,740 --> 00:12:36,720
I'm sure their families
have already burned plenty of it.

224
00:12:36,720 --> 00:12:38,080
You're so noble.

225
00:12:38,100 --> 00:12:40,160
You should burn something valuable.

226
00:12:44,050 --> 00:12:45,910
These soldiers suffered so much.

227
00:12:47,360 --> 00:12:49,320
They spent years guarding our borders,

228
00:12:49,320 --> 00:12:50,840
living on scraps,

229
00:12:50,840 --> 00:12:52,790
and facing life and death
situation every day.

230
00:12:52,790 --> 00:12:54,390
Your clothes are so fine,

231
00:12:54,590 --> 00:12:56,250
they probably never even seen

232
00:12:57,080 --> 00:12:59,170
fabric like this, let alone wore it.

233
00:13:05,510 --> 00:13:07,000
This is the finest fabric

234
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:09,060
I received for my birthday last year.

235
00:13:09,190 --> 00:13:10,510
That should be good enough

236
00:13:10,510 --> 00:13:11,510
for the soldiers.

237
00:13:13,110 --> 00:13:14,030
And these boots, these waterproof coats

238
00:13:14,030 --> 00:13:15,740
that my nanny made all by hand.

239
00:13:15,770 --> 00:13:16,970
You can have them all.

240
00:13:20,920 --> 00:13:22,800
Is that enough now?

241
00:13:33,960 --> 00:13:35,530
It should be enough.

242
00:13:37,960 --> 00:13:39,760
Except for a pair of underpants.

243
00:13:40,290 --> 00:13:42,090
Underpants are most important!

244
00:13:43,000 --> 00:13:43,950
I think...

245
00:13:43,970 --> 00:13:46,140
they might need a servant
to help out down there.

246
00:13:46,140 --> 00:13:48,200
I should burn you and send you to them.

247
00:13:50,390 --> 00:13:51,590
Why didn't you dodge?

248
00:13:51,950 --> 00:13:53,260
You say you care about them.

249
00:13:53,260 --> 00:13:54,210
Then tell me,

250
00:13:54,440 --> 00:13:55,630
what are their names?

251
00:13:55,630 --> 00:13:57,030
Where did they come from?

252
00:13:57,200 --> 00:13:57,930
I don't know.

253
00:13:59,240 --> 00:14:00,970
But Shuang may not know either.

254
00:14:01,180 --> 00:14:03,180
Every soldier in the Changfeng Army

255
00:14:03,340 --> 00:14:05,000
is registered in the records.

256
00:14:05,270 --> 00:14:06,470
If they die in battle,

257
00:14:06,750 --> 00:14:08,550
their names will be crossed off.

258
00:14:11,480 --> 00:14:12,890
Why are...

259
00:14:13,200 --> 00:14:14,840
all their names crossed out?

260
00:14:14,870 --> 00:14:17,000
They were soldiers who died in battle.

261
00:14:17,550 --> 00:14:19,010
They're no longer with us.

262
00:14:19,210 --> 00:14:21,560
So many people died in one battle.

263
00:14:21,590 --> 00:14:22,640
You're a general,

264
00:14:22,920 --> 00:14:25,040
why would you do this yourself?

265
00:14:27,840 --> 00:14:30,100
They fought alongside me for many years.

266
00:14:30,390 --> 00:14:31,720
I should remember them.

267
00:14:42,790 --> 00:14:43,750
Soldiers.

268
00:14:44,120 --> 00:14:46,520
You are all brave men
of the Changfeng Army.

269
00:14:46,750 --> 00:14:48,320
May your spirits

270
00:14:49,440 --> 00:14:50,670
protect Shuang.

271
00:14:51,390 --> 00:14:52,810
Please make her invulnerable,

272
00:14:52,810 --> 00:14:53,940
and live a long life.

273
00:14:54,450 --> 00:14:55,660
If you meet

274
00:14:55,690 --> 00:14:57,220
the King of Hell down there,

275
00:14:57,840 --> 00:14:59,570
please pass on a message for me.

276
00:14:59,660 --> 00:15:01,590
If Shuang's lifespan is cut short,

277
00:15:01,590 --> 00:15:03,450
please take mine to make up for it.

278
00:15:10,520 --> 00:15:11,920
Your wounds just healed.

279
00:15:12,130 --> 00:15:13,860
You should go back and rest now.

280
00:15:17,180 --> 00:15:17,900
Do you think

281
00:15:17,980 --> 00:15:18,460
she...

282
00:15:18,490 --> 00:15:19,560
will forgive me?

283
00:15:23,900 --> 00:15:25,450
Shuang asked me to tell you

284
00:15:26,200 --> 00:15:27,860
that she cares about you a lot.

285
00:15:30,780 --> 00:15:31,840
Of course she does!

286
00:15:32,360 --> 00:15:33,390
She's my sister!

287
00:15:33,510 --> 00:15:34,730
if she doesn't care about me,

288
00:15:34,730 --> 00:15:36,390
who else would she care about?

289
00:15:38,980 --> 00:15:39,580
By the way,

290
00:15:41,240 --> 00:15:42,300
burn them cleanly.

291
00:15:44,050 --> 00:15:45,780
That's very thoughtful of him.

292
00:15:49,270 --> 00:15:50,590
