296
00:15:56,190 --> 00:15:57,520
That's true for Li Ting,

297
00:15:57,680 --> 00:15:59,080
and it's true for you too.

298
00:16:03,330 --> 00:16:04,160
So,

299
00:16:04,880 --> 00:16:07,150
I don't have to be
a homeless anymore, right?

300
00:16:07,150 --> 00:16:08,150
You don't want to?

301
00:16:10,440 --> 00:16:12,770
There's never been a man in our residence,

302
00:16:13,050 --> 00:16:15,010
yet he's so close to Shuang.

303
00:16:16,040 --> 00:16:17,900
Could it be that Shuang and him...

304
00:16:18,390 --> 00:16:19,080
No way.

305
00:16:19,750 --> 00:16:21,720
I must find out

306
00:16:22,300 --> 00:16:24,180
who this man really is.

307
00:16:56,630 --> 00:16:57,550
It's one of us.

308
00:17:03,080 --> 00:17:03,750
Brother.

309
00:17:06,840 --> 00:17:07,480
Brother.

310
00:17:07,520 --> 00:17:08,190
Chen.

311
00:17:09,770 --> 00:17:11,250
You're finally back.

312
00:17:13,120 --> 00:17:14,030
We thought

313
00:17:14,600 --> 00:17:16,860
Empress Qin's assassins had gotten you.

314
00:17:17,840 --> 00:17:18,670
This time,

315
00:17:18,670 --> 00:17:20,770
I infiltrated Prince Annan's
funeral procession,

316
00:17:20,770 --> 00:17:21,730
and managed

317
00:17:21,790 --> 00:17:22,960
to sneak a look.

318
00:17:24,030 --> 00:17:25,430
The corpse in the coffin,

319
00:17:25,440 --> 00:17:26,510
had a damaged face,

320
00:17:26,510 --> 00:17:28,040
making it unrecognizable.

321
00:17:28,200 --> 00:17:30,000
Although the build was similar,

322
00:17:30,030 --> 00:17:31,400
there were subtle differences

323
00:17:31,400 --> 00:17:33,000
compared to Prince Annan.

324
00:17:33,339 --> 00:17:34,589
So you're saying

325
00:17:35,200 --> 00:17:37,329
that person might not be Prince Annan.

326
00:17:39,270 --> 00:17:41,200
Prince Annan might still be alive?

327
00:17:43,960 --> 00:17:45,560
Be careful, walls have ears.

328
00:17:46,640 --> 00:17:47,570
So that means...

329
00:17:47,720 --> 00:17:49,320
Prince Annan is still alive.

330
00:17:50,550 --> 00:17:51,880
Prince Annan's funeral

331
00:17:51,880 --> 00:17:53,500
was arranged entirely by Empress Qin.

332
00:17:53,500 --> 00:17:55,790
She grandly announced his death,

333
00:17:55,880 --> 00:17:56,590
and the purpose was to

334
00:17:56,590 --> 00:17:58,310
put the young prince on the throne.

335
00:17:58,310 --> 00:17:59,710
So where is Prince Annan?

336
00:18:01,680 --> 00:18:02,810
We can only hope that

337
00:18:03,360 --> 00:18:05,230
Prince Annan is just missing,

338
00:18:05,310 --> 00:18:07,040
and not in Empress Qin's hands.

339
00:18:07,640 --> 00:18:08,350
Otherwise,

340
00:18:08,350 --> 00:18:10,210
his chances of survival are slim.

341
00:18:10,240 --> 00:18:11,070
Empress Qin

342
00:18:11,310 --> 00:18:12,480
has always seen Prince Annan

343
00:18:12,480 --> 00:18:13,920
as a thorn in her side.

344
00:18:14,080 --> 00:18:15,540
We must act before she does

345
00:18:15,540 --> 00:18:17,160
and find Prince Annan quickly.

346
00:18:17,160 --> 00:18:18,750
That's easy for you to say.

347
00:18:19,070 --> 00:18:21,090
Empress Qin first
disbanded the Black Armored Army,

348
00:18:21,090 --> 00:18:22,890
and then she hunted us down.

349
00:18:22,920 --> 00:18:23,830
Only the three of us

350
00:18:23,830 --> 00:18:25,270
