00:18:36,680 --> 00:18:37,680
There's someone

353
00:18:37,960 --> 00:18:39,490
who might be able to help us.

354
00:18:41,310 --> 00:18:41,880
Who?

355
00:18:42,270 --> 00:18:44,000
Prime Minister, Zuo Chengzhi.

356
00:18:44,400 --> 00:18:46,160
He was close with Prince Annan.

357
00:18:46,850 --> 00:18:47,800
We need to find a way

358
00:18:47,800 --> 00:18:48,880
to reach Mr. Zuo.

359
00:18:49,310 --> 00:18:50,640
With his help,

360
00:18:51,400 --> 00:18:52,480
I believe

361
00:18:52,770 --> 00:18:54,030
things will be easier.

