456
00:22:21,190 --> 00:22:23,190
You deserve to die a thousand times!

457
00:22:23,270 --> 00:22:25,680
You couldn't even
manage a simple body swap,

458
00:22:25,680 --> 00:22:28,000
and now Zuo Chengzhi holds this over us!

459
00:22:29,360 --> 00:22:30,160
Your Majesty,

460
00:22:31,680 --> 00:22:33,240
Zuo Chengzhi is insolent.

461
00:22:33,480 --> 00:22:34,540
Please allow me

462
00:22:34,680 --> 00:22:35,830
