467
00:22:46,160 --> 00:22:47,830
I admit my fault.

468
00:22:52,000 --> 00:22:53,400
Since those old fools

469
00:22:53,400 --> 00:22:55,440
are so dedicated to Prince Annan,

470
00:22:55,550 --> 00:22:57,480
then I'll bring him back

471
00:22:57,720 --> 00:22:59,200
and have him work for me.

