473
00:23:04,200 --> 00:23:05,510
From now on,

474
00:23:05,920 --> 00:23:07,350
no one will ever threaten

475
00:23:07,350 --> 00:23:09,160
my son's throne again.

476
00:23:10,680 --> 00:23:11,590
Jin Wujian.

477
00:23:12,310 --> 00:23:13,400
I give you ten days.

478
00:23:17,000 --> 00:23:18,860
You can bring him back, can't you?

479
00:23:20,200 --> 00:23:21,260
Yes, Your Majesty.

480
00:23:22,680 --> 00:23:25,440
I will return with
the shadow puppet and Jade Linglong

481
00:23:25,440 --> 00:23:26,550
to see you,

482
00:23:26,920 --> 00:23:28,480
and redeem myself.

483
00:23:30,240 --> 00:23:31,200
Get lost!

