00:24:06,310 --> 00:24:07,880
Please don't blame me.

488
00:24:09,640 --> 00:24:11,310
Only by locking you tightly

489
00:24:12,270 --> 00:24:13,750
with these chains,

490
00:24:15,240 --> 00:24:16,550
can we

