495
00:24:57,850 --> 00:24:58,270
Come on.

496
00:24:58,270 --> 00:24:58,790
Sit.

497
00:25:03,310 --> 00:25:04,510
Have some soup first.

498
00:25:17,030 --> 00:25:17,830
Why are you

499
00:25:17,830 --> 00:25:18,920
