00:25:18,920 --> 00:25:19,980
and not the dishes?

501
00:25:20,110 --> 00:25:21,370
The rice is delicious.

502
00:25:21,480 --> 00:25:23,810
Even if it's good,
you can't just eat rice.

503
00:25:25,200 --> 00:25:26,110
Listen,

504
00:25:26,110 --> 00:25:27,160
now that you're
at the General's Residence,

