520
00:25:58,030 --> 00:25:59,920
The ingredients are great,

521
00:26:01,000 --> 00:26:01,720
but...

522
00:26:02,400 --> 00:26:04,260
the cooking method is a bit rough.

523
00:26:04,590 --> 00:26:05,480
These dishes...

524
00:26:05,480 --> 00:26:06,400
some too spicy,

525
00:26:06,480 --> 00:26:07,270
some too salty.

526
00:26:07,270 --> 00:26:08,720
The sweet and sour flavors are unbalanced.

527
00:26:08,720 --> 00:26:10,240
The heat is poorly controlled.

528
00:26:10,240 --> 00:26:11,350
But that's not the real problem.

529
00:26:11,350 --> 00:26:12,330
The real problem is,

530
00:26:12,330 --> 00:26:13,400
the seasonings are

531
00:26:13,420 --> 00:26:14,480
added at random.

532
00:26:14,480 --> 00:26:15,200
There's no method at all!

533
00:26:15,200 --> 00:26:17,110
It completely covered
the food's natural taste,

534
00:26:17,110 --> 00:26:18,960
leaving only blandness and fishiness.

535
00:26:18,960 --> 00:26:21,420
