the very purpose of cooking.

536
00:26:21,550 --> 00:26:23,480
I didn't realize you were so picky.

537
00:26:27,160 --> 00:26:28,490
But this bowl of rice...

538
00:26:29,400 --> 00:26:30,600
is absolutely exquisite.

539
00:26:30,600 --> 00:26:31,840
It must be

540
00:26:31,920 --> 00:26:33,580
from Lucheng's rice paddies.

541
00:26:33,740 --> 00:26:34,630
From the field

542
00:26:34,650 --> 00:26:35,720
to the bowl

543
00:26:35,750 --> 00:26:37,230
in less than half a day.

544
00:26:37,470 --> 00:26:38,880
No fancy skill needed,

545
00:26:38,920 --> 00:26:40,110
yet it's

546
00:26:40,350 --> 00:26:42,000
so soft, chewy, and tender.

547
00:26:42,000 --> 00:26:43,240
It's so fragrant and delicious.

548
00:26:43,240 --> 00:26:43,960
Perfect!

549
00:26:46,880 --> 00:26:47,920
I didn't know

550
00:26:48,410 --> 00:26:50,140
you knew so much about cooking.

551
00:26:52,920 --> 00:26:54,030
I didn't know either.

552
00:26:54,030 --> 00:26:55,440
But when I see these dishes,

553
00:26:55,440 --> 00:26:56,590
these judgments just automatically

554
00:26:56,590 --> 00:26:57,880
appear in my mind.

555
00:27:01,440 --> 00:27:02,000
Let's go.

556
00:27:02,590 --> 00:27:03,270
Where to?

557
00:27:04,000 --> 00:27:05,310
I'm taking you out to eat.

558
00:27:05,310 --> 00:27:07,640
How can you recover without proper meals?

559
00:27:08,110 --> 00:27:09,350
What would you like to eat?

560
00:27:09,350 --> 00:27:11,400
[Sixu Clinic]

561
00:27:24,160 --> 00:27:25,000
Is it spicy?

562
00:27:26,110 --> 00:27:27,510
