566
00:27:34,440 --> 00:27:37,160
Being grown-up
isn't about putting on airs.

567
00:27:37,510 --> 00:27:39,550
First, you need to learn
to care for others,

568
00:27:39,550 --> 00:27:40,830
especially your sister, Shuang,

569
00:27:40,830 --> 00:27:42,310
Don't give her so much trouble.

570
00:27:42,310 --> 00:27:43,440
Of course.

571
00:27:45,750 --> 00:27:46,350
Tell me,

572
00:27:46,790 --> 00:27:48,510
what brings you here?

573
00:27:52,280 --> 00:27:53,390
I want to ask you

574
00:27:53,750 --> 00:27:54,720
about someone.

575
00:27:58,750 --> 00:27:59,830
Take care.

576
00:28:00,270 --> 00:28:02,110
Please come again.

577
00:28:03,630 --> 00:28:04,780
Please come in.

578
00:28:05,350 --> 00:28:07,350
No wonder Manxiang Restaurant
is Lucheng's best restaurant.

579
00:28:07,350 --> 00:28:08,440
This fish tastes fresher

580
00:28:08,440 --> 00:28:10,370
than the ones right out of the lake.

581
00:28:10,880 --> 00:28:12,240
I'll accept that the fish

582
00:28:12,240 --> 00:28:13,300
is worth the price,

583
00:28:13,440 --> 00:28:15,510
but why put so much gold leaf on it?

584
00:28:15,830 --> 00:28:16,960
It's not even edible.

585
00:28:16,960 --> 00:28:17,880
Well,

586
00:28:17,880 --> 00:28:19,880
dishes should look, smell, and taste good.

587
00:28:19,880 --> 00:28:21,000
The fish is fresh and tender,

588
00:28:21,000 --> 00:28:23,110
but the color is a bit dull.

589
00:28:23,270 --> 00:28:24,680
A touch of gold leaf

590
00:28:25,000 --> 00:28:26,960
can definitely stimulate the appetite.

591
00:28:26,960 --> 00:28:28,690
It's an art on the dining table.

592
00:28:30,070 --> 00:28:31,310
Art?

593
00:28:31,460 --> 00:28:32,670
I don't really get it.

594
00:28:34,400 --> 00:28:37,110
But you seem to know a lot about this.

595
00:28:37,960 --> 00:28:39,110
Could it be...

596
00:28:39,440 --> 00:28:40,400
that you used to be

597
00:28:40,400 --> 00:28:41,680
a young master before?

598
00:28:43,960 --> 00:28:45,820
A young master from a noble family

599
00:28:46,310 --> 00:28:48,200
and a general's daughter...

600
00:28:50,280 --> 00:28:52,140
That sounds like a perfect match.

601
00:28:58,750 --> 00:28:59,830
In your dreams!

602
00:29:00,720 --> 00:29:02,780
What nonsense are you talking about?

603
00:29:04,510 --> 00:29:06,170
If I were a noble young master,

604
00:29:06,240 --> 00:29:07,840
besides knowing about food,

605
00:29:08,270 --> 00:29:10,730
I'd surely know
a thing or two about clothes.

606
00:29:11,600 --> 00:29:12,800
Shall we try?

607
00:29:17,830 --> 00:29:19,240
Please come again!

608
00:29:19,880 --> 00:29:21,830
Since you're living in my residence,

609
00:29:21,830 --> 00:29:23,660
I'll reluctantly get you

610
00:29:23,690 --> 00:29:24,690
a few outfits.

611
00:29:25,160 --> 00:29:25,750
Let's go.

612
00:29:31,230 --> 00:29:32,310
Distinguished guests,

613
00:29:32,310 --> 00:29:33,270
please come in.

614
00:29:36,880 --> 00:29:37,940
This one suits you.

615
00:29:40,270 --> 00:29:41,480
The fabric is light and thin,

616
00:29:41,480 --> 00:29:42,800
and feels smooth to the touch.

617
00:29:42,800 --> 00:29:43,640
Unfortunately,

618
00:29:43,640 --> 00:29:45,030
the weaving is poorly done,

619
00:29:45,030 --> 00:29:46,280
The cloud patterns are all messed up.

620
00:29:46,280 --> 00:29:47,610
This one suits you well.

621
00:29:47,830 --> 00:29:48,830
It looks good,

622
00:29:49,310 --> 00:29:50,000
but...

623
00:29:50,000 --> 00:29:51,340
the embroidery’s too flashy,

624
00:29:51,340 --> 00:29:52,320
too extravagant,

625
00:29:52,320 --> 00:29:53,090
not elegant.

626
00:29:55,200 --> 00:29:56,910
This one's color and fabric

627
00:29:57,100 --> 00:29:57,870
are nice.

628
00:29:59,270 --> 00:30:00,270
This one is great!

629
00:30:00,480 --> 00:30:01,640
But if I wear it in this weather,

630
00:30:01,640 --> 00:30:03,440
I'll definitely get a heat rash.

631
00:30:04,190 --> 00:30:05,990
Since you have so many opinions,

632
00:30:06,110 --> 00:30:07,170
pick one yourself.

633
00:30:10,830 --> 00:30:11,500
Go ahead.

634
00:30:24,030 --> 00:30:24,920
I'll take this one.

635
00:30:24,920 --> 00:30:26,720
Young master, you have excellent taste!

636
00:30:26,720 --> 00:30:28,310
This is our newest arrival.

637
00:30:28,310 --> 00:30:29,200
It's the most expensive

638
00:30:29,200 --> 00:30:30,550
brocade this season.

639
00:30:31,160 --> 00:30:32,790
This quality is great!

640
00:30:33,310 --> 00:30:34,790
We even have

641
00:30:34,790 --> 00:30:36,110
a ready-made outfit,

642
00:30:36,110 --> 00:30:37,770
I'll fetch it for you to try on.

643
00:30:38,000 --> 00:30:38,800
I'll go get it.

644
00:30:51,440 --> 00:30:52,840
Why are you staring at me?

645
00:30:58,750 --> 00:30:59,830
I'm just wondering

646
00:30:59,830 --> 00:31:01,430
when you became so generous.

647
00:31:01,640 --> 00:31:03,350
It's not about generosity.

648
00:31:03,920 --> 00:31:06,450
I just don't care much
about food or clothing.

649
00:31:06,550 --> 00:31:08,510
You've been at my residence for so long,

650
00:31:08,510 --> 00:31:09,880
and helped me so much.

651
00:31:10,030 --> 00:31:11,200
You even

652
00:31:11,270 --> 00:31:13,600
risked your life
to save me more than once.

653
00:31:13,830 --> 00:31:15,400
Getting you a decent outfit

654
00:31:15,510 --> 00:31:16,640
is the least I can do.

655
00:31:21,310 --> 00:31:22,710
I didn't know the General

656
00:31:23,030 --> 00:31:24,560
could say such nice things.

657
00:31:25,920 --> 00:31:27,200
What you just said

658
00:31:27,840 --> 00:31:30,240
makes me happier than getting that outfit.

659
00:31:30,550 --> 00:31:32,480
You're happy with just a few words?

660
00:31:33,030 --> 00:31:34,240
Well, that saves me money.

661
00:31:34,240 --> 00:31:36,170
Shopkeeper, about that fabric...

662
00:31:37,110 --> 00:31:39,240
I just complimented your generosity.

663
00:31:44,480 --> 00:31:45,340
Jin'an?

664
00:31:46,010 --> 00:31:48,540
You think he'd be
a good brother-in-law, too?

665
00:31:49,680 --> 00:31:50,680
Brother-in-law?

666
00:31:51,410 --> 00:31:52,870
He's just a lowly servant.

667
00:31:53,060 --> 00:31:54,860
How could he be worthy of Shuang?

668
00:31:55,400 --> 00:31:57,440
I don't like hearing you talk like that.

669
00:31:57,440 --> 00:31:59,920
All beings are equal. We all go through
life, aging, sickness, and death.

670
00:31:59,920 --> 00:32:01,550
There's no high or low status.

671
00:32:01,550 --> 00:32:03,270
Besides, he's not a servant.

672
00:32:03,400 --> 00:32:05,200
He's the one who saved your life.

673
00:32:05,790 --> 00:32:07,480
If he hadn't killed Huo Du

674
00:32:07,480 --> 00:32:08,510
and rescued you,

675
00:32:08,750 --> 00:32:09,960
would you still be here

676
00:32:09,960 --> 00:32:10,750
leisurely

677
00:32:11,110 --> 00:32:12,240
sipping tea with me?

678
00:32:13,270 --> 00:32:14,640
He killed Huo Du?

679
00:32:16,070 --> 00:32:18,200
Even though the court

680
00:32:18,200 --> 00:32:19,680
demoted your father,

681
00:32:19,680 --> 00:32:21,350
Shuang valued loyalty

682
00:32:21,350 --> 00:32:22,830
and didn't turn him in.

683
00:32:23,070 --> 00:32:24,440
That day at the residence,

684
00:32:24,440 --> 00:32:26,550
he took a strike for Shuang.

685
00:32:26,960 --> 00:32:28,270
Sharing life and death,

686
00:32:28,270 --> 00:32:29,730
it's a very touching move.

687
00:32:29,790 --> 00:32:32,050
Don't you think they'd make a good match?

688
00:32:44,570 --> 00:32:45,200
How is it?

689
00:32:59,400 --> 00:33:00,400
It suits you well.

690
00:33:00,790 --> 00:33:02,400
You're right, miss.

691
00:33:02,680 --> 00:33:03,750
Our shop

692
00:33:03,750 --> 00:33:06,070
tailors clothes for many warriors,

693
00:33:06,070 --> 00:33:08,330
and has quite the reputation in Jianghu.

694
00:33:08,510 --> 00:33:09,350
Look at him.

695
00:33:09,350 --> 00:33:11,590
Such a handsome gentleman.

696
00:33:11,590 --> 00:33:12,960
And with our clothes,

697
00:33:12,960 --> 00:33:14,880
he's even more charming.

698
00:33:23,260 --> 00:33:24,060
Miss?

699
00:33:25,680 --> 00:33:27,070
Please wrap up the old clothes,

700
00:33:27,070 --> 00:33:28,370
he'll wear this outfit.

701
00:33:28,370 --> 00:33:29,170
Sure!

702
00:33:29,830 --> 00:33:30,390
I'm on it.

703
00:33:34,400 --> 00:33:36,680
Perhaps I really was a warrior before.

704
00:33:38,090 --> 00:33:39,200
A warrior

705
00:33:40,510 --> 00:33:43,110
sounds more fitting
for a general's daughter.

706
00:33:43,370 --> 00:33:45,400
Helping the weak and saving the world.

707
00:33:45,400 --> 00:33:47,530
Robbing the rich and helping the poor.

708
00:33:48,190 --> 00:33:48,950
Indeed,

709
00:33:49,160 --> 00:33:51,020
you've robbed quite a lot from me.

710
00:33:51,350 --> 00:33:53,080
Let's forget the meal earlier.

711
00:33:53,400 --> 00:33:54,400
But for this outfit,

712
00:33:54,400 --> 00:33:55,720
we'll split the bill.

713
00:33:55,830 --> 00:33:57,200
I've already paid my share,

714
00:33:57,200 --> 00:33:59,530
and I'll deduct your part from your wages.

715
00:34:00,430 --> 00:34:01,960
Didn't you say it was a gift?

716
00:34:02,240 --> 00:34:03,270
A gift

717
00:34:03,270 --> 00:34:04,310
has its limits.

718
00:34:05,550 --> 00:34:06,680
Besides,

719
00:34:06,960 --> 00:34:08,200
didn't you just say

720
00:34:09,160 --> 00:34:11,820
you wanted to be worthy
of a general's daughter?

721
00:34:14,480 --> 00:34:15,680
Fine, deduct it then.

722
00:34:25,360 --> 00:34:26,880
You can't be unaware of

723
00:34:27,840 --> 00:34:30,100
what's happening in your family, right?

724
00:34:32,780 --> 00:34:34,190
The tea's getting cold.
I'll go heat it up for you.

725
00:34:34,190 --> 00:34:35,150
It's fine.

726
00:34:36,440 --> 00:34:38,659
Family matters never concerned me.

727
00:34:39,150 --> 00:34:41,670
My father and Shuang
have their own ways of handling things.

728
00:34:41,670 --> 00:34:43,270
If Shuang didn't turn him in,

729
00:34:44,280 --> 00:34:45,739
she must have her reasons.

730
00:34:46,360 --> 00:34:48,020
I've known you for a long time,

731
00:34:48,360 --> 00:34:51,020
but that's the first time
you've said something

732
00:34:52,360 --> 00:34:53,820
that sounds like an adult.

733
00:34:56,190 --> 00:34:56,949
Really?

734
00:34:57,070 --> 00:34:57,760
Yeah.

735
00:35:00,190 --> 00:35:02,389
There's one more thing
I want to ask, Lu.

736
00:35:02,920 --> 00:35:03,360
Go ahead.

737
00:35:03,360 --> 00:35:05,190
The smoke the assassin used that day,

738
00:35:05,190 --> 00:35:06,960
was it harmful to Shuang?

739
00:35:07,320 --> 00:35:09,320
It's just some cheap, outdated stuff,

740
00:35:09,320 --> 00:35:10,280
with a pungent smell.

741
00:35:10,280 --> 00:35:12,480
Shuang held her breath
and didn't inhale any.

742
00:35:12,480 --> 00:35:13,320
Don't worry.

743
00:35:14,030 --> 00:35:16,030
So it was low-quality stuff.

744
00:35:16,440 --> 00:35:18,670
With your advanced medical skills,

745
00:35:18,960 --> 00:35:20,920
and you love collecting rare medicines,

746
00:35:20,920 --> 00:35:22,550
I'm sure you have

747
00:35:23,280 --> 00:35:24,680
some high-quality ones.

748
00:35:24,920 --> 00:35:25,720
Show me.

749
00:35:30,110 --> 00:35:31,510
You slipped up,

750
00:35:31,840 --> 00:35:32,970
and made me unhappy,

751
00:35:33,400 --> 00:35:35,000
so you should make it up to me.

752
00:35:35,710 --> 00:35:36,770
Alright, alright,

753
00:35:37,000 --> 00:35:38,660
I'll let you have a quick look.

754
00:35:47,630 --> 00:35:49,630
This medicine is amazing.

755
00:35:50,110 --> 00:35:51,630
It looks dazzling,

756
00:35:51,630 --> 00:35:52,800
but when you put it in food,

757
00:35:52,800 --> 00:35:54,360
it disappears without a trace.

758
00:35:54,360 --> 00:35:55,360
Just a tiny bit

759
00:35:55,410 --> 00:35:57,270
can make someone sleep for hours.

760
00:35:57,710 --> 00:35:59,040
It's my secret formula.

761
00:35:59,670 --> 00:36:00,800
You're impressive.

762
00:36:03,190 --> 00:36:04,070
The tea...

763
00:36:04,190 --> 00:36:05,320
I just drank

764
00:36:05,670 --> 00:36:06,870
wasn't sweet enough.

765
00:36:07,110 --> 00:36:08,310
Do you have any sugar?

766
00:36:09,480 --> 00:36:11,290
You still have a child's taste, I see.

767
00:36:11,290 --> 00:36:11,740
Wait a moment.

768
00:36:11,740 --> 00:36:13,270
I'll add some sugar for you.

769
00:36:15,590 --> 00:36:16,720
Add plenty, please.

770
00:36:38,000 --> 00:36:38,590
General.

771
00:36:45,180 --> 00:36:46,240
Since it's going to

772
00:36:46,760 --> 00:36:48,480
be deducted from my wages anyway,

773
00:36:48,480 --> 00:36:50,340
one more won't make a difference.

774
00:37:12,190 --> 00:37:13,510
The way

775
00:37:14,110 --> 00:37:15,970
you checked the clothes earlier,

776
00:37:16,440 --> 00:37:17,630
I thought

777
00:37:19,110 --> 00:37:21,550
it might have
something to do with your past.

778
00:37:21,550 --> 00:37:22,800
If you're willing,

779
00:37:23,440 --> 00:37:25,370
whenever you remember something,

780
00:37:26,110 --> 00:37:28,040
I'll be here to uncover it with you.

781
00:37:58,870 --> 00:38:00,280
Treating yourself well sometimes

782
00:38:00,280 --> 00:38:01,740
isn't really indulgence.

783
00:38:02,430 --> 00:38:04,490
You deserve all the beautiful things

784
00:38:04,490 --> 00:38:05,450
this world has to offer.